      "role": "user",
      "content": "we checked the staging lanes and the transfer logs and everything seems to line up on paper. it's just weird. like the numbers are always slightly lower than they should be, but there's no obvious theft or breakage. it's almost like there's some kind of ghost error in the system or something. could it be a technical glitch in how the scanners pick up the individual units?",
